    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Walls or fences that are placed in a garden or orchard to protect fruit trees from wind and weather. Of varied design, they generally provide a microclimate that preserves warmth after the sun has set.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
